   <h1>The Troll&#39;s Bane Chronicle</h1>

   <h2>The third year of the new era: July</h2>

<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 1st, Sun Long points out, that the desert has grown again and that there have to be taken precautions.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 2nd, Nartak Ironmaster warns the town of different kinds of insects, which are pitching into the houses and eat the nourishments.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 3rd, the seldom occurrence happens, that the orc Robert Schwarzfu&szlig; announces, that he wants to become a monk and student of an Elarapriest.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 3rd, there was an attack committed on Fedaykins house. An arsonist set a fire, which not only threatened Fedaykin than the whole town.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 4th, Aragon intimates his engagement with Lyria Argante and that he adopts their illegitimate daughter Taaria. Once again there are sneerers and enviers. Some warn him on her.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 5th, there was sighted a remarkable glowing stone in the Skeleton-forest.  It is assumed, that it is a sign from the gods concerning their annoyance and displeasure about the damage of Falkners Hain.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 7th, Charsi the female human intimates the quainter wedding of herself and her chosen Orc Leonardo.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 7th, the librarian Sir Giandor makes a plea for a meeting of several persons, which are seeming to be connected with a crime and riots in the library, to fathom out the procedures, that happened during his absence.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 7th, a long and tragic story about the smith Fedaykin ends. After he had to fear about his life several times, because of the brother of his love in days of yore, the life of this human called Vandun found its end in a duel. Dedicated to the memory of him and his sister, graves were made.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 8th, some wanderers notice, that the beasts are no longer found at their usual places, they were gone and only appeared for targeted attacks on the town, leaving as fast as they had come.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 8th, it is intimated, that there is a thieves-guild named Shadow Thieves haunting around.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 9th, demons appeared after a long time and began to continuous attack the townspeople. Troll's Bane is troubled with attacks of flies and other vermin.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 10th, Ultoris intimates his arrangement with Fienchen. Many good wishes and praises were given.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 10th, Ferdinand Kohlberg intimates that he is going to lay down his business as a thief, aggrieved parties can come to him and can recover damages.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 10th, the townspeople begin to umulate, because of the prolonged drought. Several people fall victims to the heat and animals flee, so that the town is going hungry.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 11th, once again there are heretics making unstable accusations about Lyrenzia.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 11th, Crosis Smallburrow is urgently looking for some help for his wife Rosa Smallburrow, who was stabbed the same day. But she survived.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 13th, an attack was made on the human Ultoris. He was shot with bow and arrow by a stranger, but he just escaped being killed. Someone called Arwenia was accused therefore.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 16th, some travellers notice, that the some time ago smaller desert in the north is proliferating ceaselessly. The fear about the farmland and the water increases.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 16th, the monastery of Eldan is finished by Falk vom Wald. It is placed on the western peninsula. It is the first time that some wanderers catch sight of it and inquire about the ruins and its owner.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 16th, Elvin Shaeron founds a migratory tribe.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 16th, the Bargen Masters are resolved temporary. About one month later follows the reconstruction of the guild and the trade relation with Darlok.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 17th, the Lyrenzia Foundation convenes a meeting, to compare notes about the drought and to find relevant solutions. It will be hold on July 22nd.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 18th, Grogor intimates the foundation of one more Orc-clan. The first official act of the clan-leader is, to declare war to the other "human" Orc-clans. His clan only exists for a little while.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 21st, the public nomination of the candidates for the assignment of a public councilman of the Lyrenzia Foundation begins. Nominated are: Drogla, Dival, Zerbus and Fieps.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 23rd, the nomination phase for the two candidates, who will act for the SMACC - council begins. Nominated are: Fedaykin, Drogla and Moathia.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 25th, the elf Elvin Shaeron intimates his wedding with the female human Teranie.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 27th, Agon intimates, that the Halfling Benedickt Ackermann will be the farmer of the monastery of Eldan, from now on.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 28th, the townspeople congregate once again to speak about the Elara priestess Elaralith, which became known, for her sleazy and mysterious doings. The faith in her was liquefied and there were thoughts about denying her official title as a priestess.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 28th, Guingalan invoiced all mortal people, to group together to antagonize the malicious influences, which are impinging the isle.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 28th, Kincent Noltari founds the "Fire Seer Clan" in Troll's Bane, manifestly an old tradition of his homeland.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 28th, Darlok gives the citizens of Troll's Bane an ultimatum: Either his castle will be reconstructed, or the whole isle will fall victim to the drought. But some citizens doubt Darloks skills to dominate the drought and Dyluck invoices the citizens to refuse, because they have more to loose, than their life. Some citizen's follow Dylucks invocation, some others perform Darloks obligations.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 29th, Drathe charged Lyrenzia. He asked why the union don't do anything against their registered citizen Darlok. Others contract in his complaint. Some days later Darlok is striked off the citizens-listing.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 29th, Damien suggests a deal between the town and Darlok: Darlok will get his castle, but therefore he has to give the things he needs to conjure the drought and rot worms to some selected sages.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 30th, Darlok intimates a listing of those, who are working at the castle ruins. Some start to help, others try to sabotage the construction.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 30th, Darlok impend all those, who are disturbing the construction works, with tremendous punishments. To prove his goodwill, he alludes, that he has granted the earth to recover a bit.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 30th, Lyrenzia deputizes Damien as an official substitute with things concerning Darlok and summons asks for answers to some questions. In addition he announces an assembly of an army, to use it as leverage against Darlok.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 30th, Galim invites all dwarves in the name of Tialdin to a big festival in Silverbrand, taking place on the coming Sunday.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 31st, the armistice between the Grey Rose and Darlok is declared as broken, by Darlok. But at the moment there won't be any hostility between both parties.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 31st, the Cooperative Farmers Guild is built up again, but soon becomes inactive again, because of the disease of one of their leaders.</p>
<p>In year 3 of the new age, on July 31st, the dwarf Nartak Ironmaster, being known as traitor and spy, mysteriously dies just being captured.</p>

